HEADWORD: Superimpregnation
<hw>Su`per*im`preg*na"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The act
of impregnating, or the state of being impregnated, in addition to a
prior impregnation; superfetation.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

